24 January 2008Minister of Minerals and Energy, Buyelwa Sonjica, and Minister of Public Enterprises, Alec Erwin, will hold a media briefing tomorrow (Friday), on plans for electricity generation in South Africa.The briefing will take place as follows:Date: 25 January 2008 (Friday) Time: 09h00 Venue: Room 153, Union Buildings, PretoriaNB: There will be a video link-up at the Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town.Enquiries Harold Maloka Cell: 082 847 9799Colin Cruywagen Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)